            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#eisenbergK" start="839.860" end="x">That...that...that <a class="term" href="#vothG_wehrmacht">Wehrmacht</a> leader of the Germans, that Altoff.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="843.659" end="x">Hm.</span>
