            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#eisenbergK" start="866.911" end="x">This was going on for a long time. We were terribly tormented, and we endured very bad times. All of a sudden there began arriving in our town...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
