            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Kalman Eisenberg</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#eisenbergK" start="1130.413" end="x">I was then fifteen years old when all that happened. Also the Germans...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
