            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Kalman Eisenberg</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#eisenbergK" start="1200.742" end="x">I am Eisenberg, Kalman. My name is Eisenberg, Kalman, born in Poland in the town <a class="placename" href="#vothL78">Starachowice</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
